{"id":395558,"date":[{"year":1959,"month":9,"day":11}],"page":"6","source":"","region":"","masthead":"","special_issue":"笔会","column":"","genre":"","count":"254","ytitle":"","mtitle":"九月","ftitle":"——致保加利亚友人","authors":["田间"],"text":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"田间"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在鄂赫姆斯山崖前，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"树起雄伟的纪念碑；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"索非亚高地和平原，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"戴上千百枝红玫瑰。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"诗人伐佐夫曾说过——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"赫姆斯将是新乐园。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这预言已成为事实，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"冶金厂正火花粉飞。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"二"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"英雄们斗争五百年，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"红玫瑰才开在身边；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"从血海升起的花枝，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"盛开在革命的宫殿。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"游击队多少个战士，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"还仍然留下了笑脸；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"锐眼在守望着黑海，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"陪伴着红星和花蕊。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"三"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"季米特洛夫的儿女，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"昂起了高贵的头颅；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"威名、智慧与诗歌，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"为巴尔干绘成了彩图。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"保加利亚呵，我看见你，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"干劲十足，迈着大步。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这远隔万里的朋友，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"为你寄上祝贺的诗句!"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"1959年7月初稿"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"9月二次稿"}]}